十二岁时，羅南受邀参加电影《[[贖罪_(電影)|赎罪]]》的试镜，并获选出演少女时期的布里奥妮·泰丽思（{{lang|en|Briony Tallis}}）一角。<ref name="wildabout">{{cite web|title= Behind the Scenes of ''Atonement''|publisher= WildAboutMovies.com|url= http://www.wildaboutmovies.com/movies/AtonementMovie-AtonementTrailer-KeiraKnightleyJamesMcAvoy-FocusFeatures-2008AcademyAwar.php|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaA5EhPZ?url=http://www.wildaboutmovies.com/movies/AtonementMovie-AtonementTrailer-KeiraKnightleyJamesMcAvoy-FocusFeatures-2008AcademyAwar.php|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 4 February 2010}}</ref>她在片中与[[凯拉·奈特利|凯拉·奈特利]]和[[詹姆斯·麦卡沃伊|詹姆斯·麦卡沃伊]]合作，受到导演[[乔·莱特|乔·莱特]]的喜爱。<ref name="wildabout"/>这部成本为三千万美元的电影最终在全球席卷一亿三千万美元的票房，也获得了数个奖项和提名，在商业和艺术上取得了双重成功。<ref>{{cite web|title= ''Atonement''|publisher= [[The_Numbers_(website)|The-Numbers.com]]|url= http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2007/ATONE.php|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaAaRvtT?url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2007/ATONE.php|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 4 February 2010}}</ref>羅南的表演广受赞誉，获得了[[英国电影学院奖最佳女配角|英国电影学院奖]]、[[金球獎最佳電影女配角|金球獎]]和[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|奥斯卡最佳女配角奖]]提名，成为最年轻的十位奥斯卡女配提名获得者之一。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.filmsite.org/bestsuppactress.html|title= Academy Awards Best Supporting Actress Facts & Trivia|first= Tim|last= Dirks|year= 2013|publisher= [[Filmsite.org|Filmsite.org]]|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6Ha7AcRJM?url=http://www.filmsite.org/bestsuppactress.html|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 22 June 2013}}</ref>

羅南的下一部作品是2007年的[[浪漫喜剧|浪漫喜剧片]]《{{le|情不自禁愛上你|I Could Never Be Your Woman}}》。该片因资金问题[[录影带首映|直接发行了DVD]]，<ref>{{cite web|first= Missy|last= Schwartz|title= Would You Dump This Woman?|work= [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|url= http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20175469,00.html|date= 8 February 2008|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaBd3MJL?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20175469,00.html|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 4 February 2010}}</ref>反响平淡。<ref>{{cite web|first= Joe|last= Leydon|title= ''I Could Never Be Your Woman''|work= [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|url= http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117936281?refcatid=31|date= 21 February 2008|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110513122442/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117936281?refcatid=31|archivedate= 2011-05-13|deadurl= yes|accessdate= 4 February 2010}}</ref>2008年，她参演了电影《{{le|魔幻奇緣|Death Defying Acts}}》和《[[微光城市－黑暗之光首部曲|微光城市－黑暗之光首部曲]]》，她在前者中的表现为她赢得了一项{{link-en|爱尔兰电影电视学院奖|Irish Film & Television Academy}}。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.ifta.ie/winners/iftawinners2009.html|title= Winners of the 6th Annual Irish Film & Television Awards|year= 2010|publisher= The Irish Film & Television Academy|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6Ha5s1l5W?url=http://www.ifta.ie/winners/iftawinners2009.html|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= yes|accessdate= 22 June 2013}}</ref>《魔幻奇緣》受到的评价毁誉参半，票房失利，全球总票房仅有八百万美元。<ref>{{cite web|title=''Death Defying Acts'' (2007)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_defying_acts/|accessdate=4 February 2010|archive-date=2015-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822064402/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_defying_acts/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title= ''Death Defying Acts''|publisher= [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=deathdefyingacts.htm|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaCPFmct?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=deathdefyingacts.htm|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 4 February 2010}}</ref>奇幻片《微光城市－黑暗之光首部曲》改编自[[琴娜·杜普洛|琴娜·杜普洛]]的同名小说，评价不一，票房表现也很糟糕，远低于投资。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_of_ember/|title = ''City of Ember'' (2008)|publisher = Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate = 13 September 2010|archive-date = 2010-08-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100831142417/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_of_ember/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=cityofember.htm|title= ''City of Ember''|publisher= Box Office Mojo|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaCZWRpa?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=cityofember.htm|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 20 February 2010}}</ref>

2009年，羅南主演了[[彼得·杰克逊|彼得·杰克逊]]的影片《[[可爱的骨头|可爱的骨头]]》，其他参演的明星有[[麗素·慧絲|麗素·慧絲]]、[[馬克·華伯格|馬克·華伯格]]、[[蘇珊·莎蘭登|蘇珊·莎蘭登]]和[[史丹利·特治|史丹利·特治]]。她的角色是一个十四岁的女孩，被奸杀后在想象中的天国注视自己的亲友面对接下来的生活。羅南和家人起初因电影涉及的主题对接受该角色感到犹豫，但在与彼得·杰克逊见面后同意出演，导演称她“在银幕上看上去棒极了”。<ref name="latimesronaninterview">{{cite web|url= http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-saoirse10-2009dec10,0,4409476.story|work= [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date= 10 December 2009|first= Yvonne|last= Villarreal|title= Saoirse Ronan of ''The Lovely Bones'' stays on balance|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaCtzzDJ?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/dec/10/entertainment/la-et-saoirse10-2009dec10|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 28 December 2009}}</ref>尽管影片收到了部分差评，<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.newser.com/story/75915/lovely-bones-hits-and-misses.html|title= ''Lovely Bones'', Hits and Misses|first= Rob|last= Quinn|date= 11 December 2009|publisher= [[Newser|Newser]]|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaDEOJR3?url=http://www.newser.com/story/75915/lovely-bones-hits-and-misses.html|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 27 February 2010}}</ref>但羅南的表演还是受评论界称赞，她赢得了[[评论家选择奖|评论家选择奖]]最佳年轻演员奖、[[土星獎|土星獎]]最佳年轻演员奖，并收获了[[英国电影学院奖最佳女主角|英国电影学院奖最佳女主角]]提名。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://awards.bafta.org/award/2010/film/leading-actress|title= Leading Actress in 2010|publisher= [[British_Academy_of_Film_and_Television_Arts|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]]|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6Ha6QEne6?url=http://awards.bafta.org/award/2010/film/leading-actress|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 22 June 2013}}</ref>

