ws/hanna-20110407|work=Rolling Stone|title=Hanna|date=7 April 2011|first=Peter|last=Travers|accessdate=7 November 2013|archive-date=2016-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120114656/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/hanna-20110407|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，她为[[米林宏昌|米林宏昌]]的动画片《[[借物少女艾莉緹|借物少女艾莉緹]]》中的女主角英國版配音。<ref name="English-cast2">{{cite web | url = http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-06-21/arrietty-to-have-different-dub-casts-in-u.s-u.k | title = Ghibli's ''Arrietty'' to Have Different Dub Casts in U.S., U.K. | publisher = Anime News Network | date = 21 June 2011 | accessdate = 13 July 2011 | archive-date = 2016-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120114656/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2011-06-21/arrietty-to-have-different-dub-casts-in-u.s-u.k | dead-url = no }}</ref>羅南曾考虑出演《[[哈比人电影系列|哈比人]]》电影系列中的一位[[精灵|精灵]]，<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/news/saoirse-ronans-hobbit-holiday-15151475.html|title= Saoirse Ronan's ''Hobbit'' holiday|work= [[The_Belfast_Telegraph|The Belfast Telegraph]]|date= 5 May 2011|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaGTDm48?url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/news/saoirse-ronans-hobbit-holiday-28614458.html|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 26 December 2012}}</ref>但最终因档期原因退出。<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=30916|first= Phil|last= de Semlyen|title= Saoirse Ronan Not In ''The Hobbit''|work= [[Empire_(film_magazine)|Empire]]|date= 9 May 2011|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/6HaI051kB?url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=30916|archivedate= 2013-06-23|deadurl= no|accessdate= 26 December 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.mtv.com/videos/movies/640280/saoirse-ronan-has-always-fancied-being-an-elf-in-the-hobbit.jhtml|title= Saoirse Ronan Has 'Always Fancied' Being An Elf In ''The Hobbit''|publisher= MTV|date= 7 April 2011|deadurl= no|accessdate= 26 December 2012|archive-date= 2011-04-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110411011921/http://www.mtv.com/videos/movies/640280/saoirse-ronan-has-always-fancied-being-an-elf-in-the-hobbit.jhtml}}</ref>

